# The ECB SDMX API used by this collector is PUBLIC and KEYLESS — no secret is required
# to run it. This file is included per the assignment deliverables (section 8): keep real
# secrets in a local `.env` (git-ignored) and commit only this example.
#
# If you point the collector at a source that needs a key (e.g. the CNB ARAD API), add it
# to your environment or local `.env`, and never commit `.env`:
# ARAD_API_KEY=your-free-key-here
#
# Optional override read directly by kinea.config (export it in your shell or load this
# file with your preferred environment manager):
# KINEA_ECB_BASE_URL=https://data-api.ecb.europa.eu/service/data
